works.description: Multidisciplinary design firm Studio Dror has now teamed up with the car maker Acura to create a limited edition desk dubbed the S.H.I.E.L.D. Agent. The desk draws inspiration from the automaker’s role in Thor, the new movie starring Chris Hemsworth, Natalie Portman and Anthony Hopkins. In the movie, the agents of the S.H.I.E.L.D. intelligence and security organization of the Marvel Universe are seen driving the Acura TL, MDX, ZDX and RL models. Taking note of the same,
